To use ollama, add in the `__main__.py`  the secrets:

- OLLAMA_HOST
- AUTH

When you need to access Ollama, retrieve the secrets from args and build the url f"https://{AUTH}@{OLLAMA_HOST}"

Then use `requests` to invoke the Ollama API.
By default add stream false to both API requests



